{"tid":2177520,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"全城黑衣　家長身教誠實　 港人：我們不會遺忘7.21","createTime":"2020-08-27T18:58:36.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-27T23:57:43.000Z","uid":240362,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"38c0465750d4071c778fc0baddce95e2afbcbb7e","tid":2177520,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-27T18:58:36.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200828/747MLJXZ5RETRH7GZDZLIILTDI/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200828%2F747MLJXZ5RETRH7GZDZLIILTDI%2F&d=Bx5vHrS2V4FMjGMjdccONqCH8iT5eEApQhURqQe1KTk%3D&h=3fd7a444\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200828%2F747MLJXZ5RETRH7GZDZLIILTDI%2F&h=243645ec\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200828/747MLJXZ5RETRH7GZDZLIILTDI/</a><br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】警方前日以涉嫌暴動罪拘捕追查7.21元朗恐襲真相的立法會議員林卓廷，更在記招推出四大警謊竄改7.21歷史，昨日不少人響應「全城黑衣」行動，對警方歪理表達不滿。本報走訪各區，市民狠批警謊侮辱港人智慧，顛倒是非黑白，要身體力行向政權指鹿為馬說不，慨嘆穿黑衣是「配合返𠵱家社會嘅黑暗」，批評警隊成為政權工具，與市民越走越遠。有父母為女兒換去平日的花花裙，一家改穿黑衫、黑裙逛街，為的是要把真相傳承予下一代，力拒我們的家變成荒謬之都。"},{"pid":"c4e3b7fbe8a5dedb9c581fceb9b34dab61cd4b34","tid":2177520,"uid":354682,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-27T23:57:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/noodles.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/noodles.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/noodles.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/noodles.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/noodles.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}